reviewText: Excellent program! I still watch it today as a reminder to check my results and to make sure I haven't had any lapses in discipline when it comes to my health and my finances. I frequently recommend this program to college students and adults who are struggling.  You can save yourself the investment in a live seminar and get this DVD instead.
This DVD helped me transform my life. And this is because I watch it every week. So don't just buy it and let it seat on your desk. You need to take actions. Jim Rohn is simply the best.
